      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Spectra from any source that could not be linked to valid SMILES strings were not included. Included species were limited to those that existed as a single molecule (e.g., excluding mixtures and salts). Species were also limited to contain only the following atoms: C, H, O, N, Si, P, S, F, Cl, Br, and I.",
