      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Chemprop-IR software is available through a public repository with Git Hub... An archived version of the software and the trained models associated with this publication are shared through Zenodo.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms condition (1) and (3) are met (public repo, clear interface between MPNN fingerprint and phase feature concatenation). However, the paper does not explicitly articulate condition (2) as a prerequisite or methodology step; it is implicit in the work rather than stated as a trigger condition.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10_1021_acs_jcim_1c00055",
