      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Instantiate a PyTorch message passing neural network model (such as chemprop-IR) with integrated spectral feature modules, then execute a forward pass on molecular graph or SMILES inputs to verify model compilation, parameter flow, and output tensor shapes.",
